L(\theta \mid \boldsymbol Z) = \prod_{i=1}^n p_i^{Z_i} (1-p_i)^{1-Z_i} = e^{-n\bar Z/\theta} (1-e^{-1/\theta})^{n(1-\bar Z)}.
\ell(\theta \mid \boldsymbol Z) = -\frac{n \bar Z}{\theta} + n(1-\bar Z) \log(1-e^{-1/\theta}).
